part.description:
HENGST OE REPLACEMENT OIL FILTER

Constructed with service-friendly, robust materials for optimal filtration and long product life, Hengst OE Replacement oil filter delivers reliable protection against engine contaminants. It facilitates proper lubrication of moving parts and provides clean oil supply to engine components.

  • Resistant to pressure of up to 20 bar and withstands temperature of up to 160°C
  • Extremely durable design with replaceable filter insert
  • Effectively removes metal abrasions, dust and other residues down to 10 μm (0.01 mm)
  • Offers clean oil supply to minimize emissions and fuel consumption
  • Prevents premature wear of engine components

Founded in 1958, Hengst is a world-renowned manufacturer of top-quality filtration products for marine applications, agricultural equipment and passenger cars.

  • System contains two air springs, air lines, Schrader valves and hardware
